## [INFRA CONTRACTS]
- Redis: AOF persistence ONLY — `appendonly yes`, `appendfsync always`
- Postgres: advisory locks for lane exclusivity — `pg_try_advisory_lock(laneId)`
- NonceManager: centralized at `@packages/core/src/infra/nonce-manager.ts`
- CircuitBreaker: centralized at `@packages/core/src/infra/circuit-breaker.ts`
- All env vars: loaded via `@packages/core/src/config/env.ts` — never `process.env` inline

---

## [TESTING CONTRACT]
- Every Sentinel function MUST have a unit test with mocked provider
- Every integration test MUST use Tenderly fork — never mainnet
- Test file naming: `<sentinel>.test.ts` co-located with source
- Use `vitest` — not Jest
- Mock pattern: `vi.fn()` for all external calls — no real HTTP in unit tests

